        "text": [
          " سَمِعْتُ أَبَا الْحَسَنِ الرِّضَا ع کَانَ یَقُولُ مَنْ قَالَ لَا حَوْلَ وَ لَا قُوَّهَ إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ الْعَلِیِّ الْعَظِیمِ دَفَعَ اللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ بِهَا عَنْهُ سَبْعِینَ نَوْعاً مِنَ الْبَلَاءِ أَیْسَرُهَا الْخَنْقُ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
            "1.  It is narrated that Imam Ja’far Sadiq (a.s.) said, “Allah, the Mighty and Sublime will remove seventy types of calamities from  the  one  who says  ‘Laa  h’aula  wa  laa  quwwata  illaa billaahil a’liyyil a’z’eem’ the least of which is death due to suffocation.”"
          ]
        }
      }
